`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Enchantment
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'enchant armor'
 * cast 'enchant weapon'

 These spells allow Sorcerers to imbue weapons and armor with magical power to
make them more effective.  There is a chance, however, that the enchantment
will fail and render the item worse than it was before or even destroy the
item.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
